{{Geography of Romania}}
This is a '''list of protected areas of [[Romania]]'''.

About 5.18% of the area of Romania has a protected  status (12,360&nbsp;km²), including the [[Danube Delta]], which makes half of these areas (2.43% of Romania's area).

