;Compilation films

Between 1980 and 1981, two [[compilation film]]s were produced. Each of these comprised re-edited versions of four of the original episodes. The films were produced for the American market and aired in the United States as part of an [[ITC Entertainment]] package titled "Super Space Theater"; other Supermarionation series were given similar treatments. On 24 November ([[Thanksgiving]]) 1988, the second ''Stingray'' compilation feature, ''Invaders from the Deep'', appeared as the first broadcast episode of movie-mocking TV series ''[[Mystery Science Theater 3000]]'' in the US.

